  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd 5 \u0ba4\u0bae\u0bbf\u0bb4\u0b95 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "5 more Tamil Nadu fishermen arrested",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Five fishermen from Tamil Nadu have been arrested by the navy on charges of fishing across the border.",
        "The five fishermen from Pudukottai district's Jegatapattinam area, who left Kodiakkarai area in a boat to catch fish, were arrested by the navy on Monday while they were fishing across the border at Karainagar beach in Jaffna.",
        "The Navy has taken steps to present the arrested fishermen in the Home Guard Magistrate's Court through the Department of Fisheries and Aquatic Resources on Tuesday.",
        "Meanwhile, the 12 Tamil Nadu fishermen who were arrested for the crime of fishing across the border on Sunday, has been ordered to be remanded until the next 08th.",
        "17 Tamil Nadu fishermen have been arrested for crossing the border in two days."
      ],
